(41, 6, 48, 18, 9, 8, 8, NULL, 'Divine Authority Over Nature', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine control over the sea. Both passages emphasize the act of treading upon the waves, illustrating God''s power over nature.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
